1
00:00:10,719 --> 00:00:13,888
Jonathan! Nancy! Jonathan!

2
00:00:14,764 --> 00:00:16,349
Jonathan! Nancy!

3
00:00:18,435 --> 00:00:19,436
Ano ba'ng ginagawa mo?

4
00:00:19,519 --> 00:00:22,689
Makinig kayo! Wag n'yong gagalawin 'yan!

5
00:00:36,536 --> 00:00:37,787
Baka di mo natamaan?

6
00:00:54,763 --> 00:00:56,723
-Kailangan na nating…
-Oo nga.

7
00:01:40,725 --> 00:01:43,353
Bago po kayo magsalita,
alam kong alas-singko pa lang,

8
00:01:43,436 --> 00:01:45,396
pero kailangan ko ng telemetry tracker.

9
00:01:45,480 --> 00:01:47,273
Ano? Erica, alas—

10
00:01:47,357 --> 00:01:49,359
Alas-singko. Sinabi na nga niya, pare.

11
00:01:49,442 --> 00:01:51,611
Teka nga. Sino ka ba?

12
00:01:51,694 --> 00:01:53,738
-Tito ko.
-Babysitter. Babysitter.

13
00:01:53,822 --> 00:01:55,115
Sino sila, snookums?

14
00:01:55,198 --> 00:01:59,035
Wala 'to, sugar loaf. Matulog ka na ulit.
Sandali lang 'to.

15
00:01:59,119 --> 00:02:00,328
Okay.

16
00:02:00,411 --> 00:02:01,663
'Yong librarian?

17
00:02:01,746 --> 00:02:03,832
Pag maingay ka sa kama,
pinapatahimik ka niya?

18
00:02:03,915 --> 00:02:10,171
Okay. Ikaw at kung sino ka man,
kabastusan 'tong ginagawa n'yo.

19
00:02:10,255 --> 00:02:12,465
Magkita na lang tayo sa klase, Erica.

20
00:02:13,466 --> 00:02:15,343
Nasa panganib si Dustin.

21
00:02:16,010 --> 00:02:18,138
Panganib? Anong klaseng panganib?

22
00:02:18,221 --> 00:02:19,848
'Yong tipong puwede siyang mamatay.

23
00:02:19,931 --> 00:02:23,017
Ano sa tingin mo, snookums?
Makikipaglaro ka lang ba kay bookworm,

24
00:02:23,101 --> 00:02:26,062
o gagawa ka ng tracker
para iligtas 'yong star student mo?

25
00:02:29,232 --> 00:02:30,233
Henderson!

26
00:02:30,942 --> 00:02:32,068
Dustin!

27
00:02:32,152 --> 00:02:33,528
Dustin. Uy.

28
00:02:33,611 --> 00:02:34,737
Ano ba 'yon?

29
00:02:34,821 --> 00:02:36,990
'Yong shield generator ba 'yon?
Nahanap nila?

30
00:02:37,073 --> 00:02:38,116
Nagkamali ako.

31
00:02:38,825 --> 00:02:40,076
Napaka…

32
00:02:41,619 --> 00:02:43,037
laki ng pagkakamali ko.

33
00:02:43,121 --> 00:02:44,205
Ano?

34
00:02:44,289 --> 00:02:46,332
Pagkaalis mo, may nakita 'kong journal.

35
00:02:47,041 --> 00:02:48,626
Journal ni Brenner.

36
00:02:50,170 --> 00:02:53,381
Nasa lab na 'to 'yong susi
na sisira sa pader,

37
00:02:53,464 --> 00:02:56,050
pero hindi 'yon shield generator.

38
00:02:56,134 --> 00:02:58,636
Hindi dark magic 'yon.
Hindi si Vecna ang gumawa no'n.

39
00:03:02,056 --> 00:03:03,391
Gawa ng science 'yon.

40
00:03:04,809 --> 00:03:08,396
Exotic matter ang tawag
ng mga theoretical physicists do'n.

41
00:03:08,479 --> 00:03:12,066
'Yon ang pinanggagalingan ng lakas
na humahawak sa higanteng pader na 'yon,

42
00:03:12,150 --> 00:03:14,569
at mukhang binaril yata ni Nancy 'yon.

43
00:03:25,496 --> 00:03:28,541
Masama ba 'yon? Kaya nga tayo nandito
para mapasok 'yong pader.

44
00:03:28,625 --> 00:03:29,459
Di ka nakikinig!

45
00:03:29,542 --> 00:03:31,669
-Nakikinig ako.
-Di si Vecna ang gumawa no'n.

46
00:03:31,753 --> 00:03:33,254
Wala siya sa kabila,

47
00:03:33,338 --> 00:03:35,381
kaya wala rin do'n si Holly
at 'yong mga bata.

48
00:03:35,465 --> 00:03:36,299
Walang tao do'n.

49
00:03:37,675 --> 00:03:39,636
Ano'ng nasa kabila ng pader?

50
00:03:49,812 --> 00:03:51,105
Bakit huminto?

51
00:03:57,779 --> 00:04:00,031
Dustin, ano'ng nasa kabila ng pader?

52
00:04:00,657 --> 00:04:01,658
Kamatayan.

53
00:04:11,834 --> 00:04:14,087
Umalis na tayo! Tara na!

54
00:04:15,421 --> 00:04:16,798
Bilis! Bilis! Bilis!

55
00:04:17,507 --> 00:04:18,633
Takbo! Takbo!

56
00:04:19,342 --> 00:04:20,468
Yumuko kayo!

57
00:04:30,687 --> 00:04:32,397
Itong buong panahong 'to,

58
00:04:32,480 --> 00:04:35,650
lahat ng inakala natin
tungkol sa Upside Down,

59
00:04:36,484 --> 00:04:37,944
mali pala.

60
00:04:42,991 --> 00:04:44,033
'Yong gate!

61
00:04:44,617 --> 00:04:45,743
'Yong gate!

62
00:04:46,869 --> 00:04:48,663
Gagawa ako ng daan!

63
00:04:48,746 --> 00:04:52,834
Hindi! Dito ka lang!
Dito ka lang sa likod ko!

64
00:04:52,917 --> 00:04:54,919
Wag! Punyeta naman, o!

65
00:05:04,345 --> 00:05:05,346
Tama na!

66
00:05:06,014 --> 00:05:07,056
Wag!

67
00:05:19,777 --> 00:05:22,405
Itong lugar na 'to, itong Upside Down,

68
00:05:22,488 --> 00:05:24,324
hindi ito ibang dimension,

69
00:05:24,407 --> 00:05:25,992
hindi ito ibang mundo.

70
00:05:26,075 --> 00:05:27,702
Wormhole 'to.

71
00:05:27,785 --> 00:05:28,786
Tulay 'to

72
00:05:29,662 --> 00:05:33,791
sa pagitan ng dalawang time at space,
sa pagitan ng mundo natin at ng isa pa.

73
00:05:33,875 --> 00:05:35,460
At kapag gumuho 'yong tulay?

74
00:05:35,543 --> 00:05:36,961
Kasama tayong guguho.

75
00:05:39,922 --> 00:05:41,049
Lahat tayo.

76
00:07:03,464 --> 00:07:10,471
CHAPTER SIX:
PAGTAKAS SA CAMAZOTZ

77
00:07:41,043 --> 00:07:42,503
Pasok na!

78
00:07:47,467 --> 00:07:50,386
Ayos ka lang? Ayos ka lang?
Wag kang matakot.

79
00:07:51,179 --> 00:07:53,306
Ligtas tayo dito.
Di niya tayo malalapitan dito.

80
00:07:53,389 --> 00:07:54,432
Max…

81
00:08:03,858 --> 00:08:05,109
Holly!

82
00:08:05,860 --> 00:08:06,861
Halika.

83
00:08:10,781 --> 00:08:11,866
Holly, iha.

84
00:08:11,949 --> 00:08:14,202
Tumigil ka, kung hindi sasaktan ko siya.

85
00:08:16,204 --> 00:08:20,416
Alam kong naniniwala ka
na kaibigan mo si Max.

86
00:08:21,042 --> 00:08:25,254
Pero pinaikot ka lang niya, Holly.
Ginulo niya ang isip mo.

87
00:08:25,338 --> 00:08:27,215
Sinungaling siya!

88
00:08:27,298 --> 00:08:29,634
Hindi! Hindi, ikaw ang sinungaling!

89
00:08:29,717 --> 00:08:32,011
Nakita kita! Nakita ko kung ano ka talaga!

90
00:08:32,094 --> 00:08:35,306
Halimaw ka! Nakakadiring halimaw!

91
00:08:35,389 --> 00:08:36,849
Holly!

92
00:08:36,933 --> 00:08:40,520
Kapag di ka sumama sa 'kin
at bumalik kasama ng ibang bata,

93
00:08:40,603 --> 00:08:43,272
mapipilitan akong saktan si Max.

94
00:08:47,026 --> 00:08:49,153
Baka nga patayin ko pa siya.

95
00:08:49,237 --> 00:08:51,405
Ba't di mo gawin? Ha?

96
00:08:52,031 --> 00:08:53,074
Eto ako, o.

97
00:08:53,157 --> 00:08:54,909
Ay, oo nga pala.

98
00:08:54,992 --> 00:08:59,288
Takot ka nga pala
sa pesteng kuweba na 'to, duwag!

99
00:08:59,956 --> 00:09:02,792
Iba na ngayon, Max.

100
00:09:03,834 --> 00:09:07,255
May iba nang paraan
para makalapit ako sa 'yo.

101
00:09:07,838 --> 00:09:08,839
At ikaw, Holly.

102
00:09:09,966 --> 00:09:13,177
Sa oras na pahirapan ko
ang bago mong kaibigan,

103
00:09:14,595 --> 00:09:16,180
at pahihirapan ko siya,

104
00:09:16,931 --> 00:09:20,351
puwede kang bumalik sa 'kin
at tapusin ang paghihirap niya,

105
00:09:21,018 --> 00:09:23,396
o kaya panoorin mo siyang mamatay.

106
00:09:24,230 --> 00:09:26,274
Nasa mga kamay mo ang buhay niya.

107
00:10:10,401 --> 00:10:14,947
Ipaliwanag n'yo nga sa 'kin
kung ano'ng nangyari kanina.

108
00:10:15,031 --> 00:10:16,574
Sinunog na natin 'yong particles.

109
00:10:16,657 --> 00:10:18,743
Nakita kong nagliparan 'yon
pataas sa tower.

110
00:10:18,826 --> 00:10:21,245
-Nakita n'yo naman, di ba?
-Kitang-kita.

111
00:10:21,329 --> 00:10:23,623
Di na dapat konektado si Will
sa hive mind.

112
00:10:23,706 --> 00:10:25,791
-Theoretically.
-Ba't di siya nagising?

113
00:10:25,875 --> 00:10:28,919
Pa'no niya nakita si Max
kung kasama ni Max si Holly? Totoo ba 'to?

114
00:10:29,003 --> 00:10:30,630
Ginugulo na naman ba tayo ni Vecna?

115
00:10:30,713 --> 00:10:32,506
Sobrang labo, e!

116
00:10:32,590 --> 00:10:37,094
Hindi maintindihan ng mga doktor
kung bakit na-coma si Max, di ba?

117
00:10:37,178 --> 00:10:38,721
Ano? Hindi. Bakit?

118
00:10:40,848 --> 00:10:43,934
Okay. Okay, okay, okay.

119
00:10:44,018 --> 00:10:47,730
Ipagpalagay muna natin
na totoo lahat ng nakita ni Will.

120
00:10:47,813 --> 00:10:50,066
-Nakita niya si Max, si Holly.
-Okay, pero pa'no?

121
00:10:50,149 --> 00:10:53,194
Ipapaliwanag ko. Kunwari…

122
00:10:54,070 --> 00:10:55,321
ito si Will,

123
00:10:55,404 --> 00:10:58,824
ito naman si Holly.

124
00:10:58,908 --> 00:10:59,784
Tapos…

125
00:11:00,910 --> 00:11:03,621
siyempre, ito si Max.

126
00:11:04,580 --> 00:11:07,291
Nasa magkakaibang lugar sila,
sa Squawk, sa ospital,

127
00:11:07,375 --> 00:11:09,752
at sa di pa natin alam na lugar
sa Upside Down. Tama?

128
00:11:09,835 --> 00:11:11,045
-Tama.
-Oo.

129
00:11:11,128 --> 00:11:14,799
Pero may isang super importanteng bagay
na pare-pareho sa kanila.

130
00:11:14,882 --> 00:11:16,217
Wala silang malay.

131
00:11:18,719 --> 00:11:22,056
-Ano'ng mangyayari pag kinuha ka ni Vecna?
-Mawawalan ka ng malay.

132
00:11:22,139 --> 00:11:24,225
Magmumukha kang na-coma.

133
00:11:24,308 --> 00:11:27,478
Kaya pala di maipaliwanag ng mga doktor.
Hindi na-coma si Max.

134
00:11:27,561 --> 00:11:29,188
Wala siyang malay.

135
00:11:29,772 --> 00:11:32,692
Kagaya ni Will. Kagaya ni Holly.

136
00:11:33,275 --> 00:11:36,487
Malinaw na,
kasinglinaw ng birit ni Whitney Houston.

137
00:11:36,570 --> 00:11:38,155
Pa'no kung 'yong diwa nila

138
00:11:39,281 --> 00:11:40,700
ay nasa iisang lugar?

139
00:11:41,784 --> 00:11:43,077
Sa isip ni Vecna.

140
00:11:44,453 --> 00:11:45,538
Nakakulong.

141
00:11:46,580 --> 00:11:48,290
O kaya galing sila do'n.

142
00:11:48,374 --> 00:11:49,583
Kung tama si Will,

143
00:11:49,667 --> 00:11:53,754
si Max at si Holly,
sinusubukan na nilang tumakas.

144
00:11:53,838 --> 00:11:55,297
At kung magagawa nila 'yon,

145
00:11:55,381 --> 00:11:58,759
makakabalik sila sa katawan nila,

146
00:11:59,552 --> 00:12:02,388
tapos magigising na si Max.

147
00:12:02,471 --> 00:12:05,266
Literal na nasa isip sila ni Vecna.

148
00:12:05,349 --> 00:12:07,852
-Alam nila lahat, kung nasa'n si Will.
-Pati mga bata.

149
00:12:07,935 --> 00:12:10,438
-Alam nila 'yong plano niya.
-'Yon na ang endgame.

150
00:12:10,521 --> 00:12:12,732
Nakasalalay ang kapalaran ng planeta

151
00:12:12,815 --> 00:12:16,402
sa mga kamay ng comatose mong girlfriend
at sa bunsong kapatid mo.

152
00:12:16,485 --> 00:12:18,904
-Wala namang mawawala, di ba?
-Kaya mong mag-drive?

153
00:12:18,988 --> 00:12:19,947
Hindi nga lang legal.

154
00:12:20,030 --> 00:12:22,116
Sige. 'Yong kotse ni Joyce.
Wag kang papahuli.

155
00:12:22,199 --> 00:12:23,701
Kayo kay Max. Dito ako kay Will.

156
00:12:23,784 --> 00:12:24,910
Okay.

157
00:13:04,116 --> 00:13:06,160
Naaalala mo ba ang lugar na 'to…

158
00:13:07,787 --> 00:13:08,662
William?

159
00:13:13,209 --> 00:13:16,837
Bumabalik ba sa 'yo…

160
00:13:21,383 --> 00:13:22,593
ang mga alaala?

161
00:13:23,719 --> 00:13:25,638
Si Max. Si Holly.

162
00:13:27,139 --> 00:13:28,808
Nakatakas sila, 'no?

163
00:13:30,226 --> 00:13:32,228
Bumagal ka ba dahil sa binti mo?

164
00:13:32,311 --> 00:13:35,397
Akala mo matalino ka na?

165
00:13:35,981 --> 00:13:41,320
Baka nakakalimutan mo, ako 'yon.

166
00:13:41,904 --> 00:13:44,365
Ako ang nagpapasok sa 'yo dito.

167
00:13:45,491 --> 00:13:48,285
Naging kasangkapan kita.

168
00:13:49,245 --> 00:13:50,746
Naging espiya kita.

169
00:13:52,331 --> 00:13:54,083
Ikaw ang naging tagabuo ko.

170
00:13:55,376 --> 00:13:56,377
Tagabuo?

171
00:13:59,755 --> 00:14:03,217
Sa tingin mo, pa'no nabuo
ang mga lagusan, William?

172
00:14:05,886 --> 00:14:08,889
Ikaw ang gumawa ng mga 'yon

173
00:14:08,973 --> 00:14:13,561
sa bawat gabing natutulog ka.

174
00:14:19,984 --> 00:14:22,820
Malaki ang taglay mong kapangyarihan.

175
00:14:23,654 --> 00:14:26,365
Pero wag kang magkakamali, bata.

176
00:14:27,449 --> 00:14:30,327
Kapangyarihan ko 'yon,

177
00:14:30,411 --> 00:14:34,623
at mas higit pa itong malakas kaysa dati.

178
00:14:38,961 --> 00:14:41,547
Mas malakas pa.

179
00:14:51,974 --> 00:14:54,268
Sa wakas, panahon na.

180
00:14:55,394 --> 00:15:01,066
Panahon na para dalhin tayo
ng mga kasangkapan ko sa bagong mundo.

181
00:15:02,860 --> 00:15:04,403
Sa mas magandang mundo.

182
00:15:05,321 --> 00:15:09,992
Malas mo dahil ang mundo mo,
hindi 'yon magiging totoo

183
00:15:10,075 --> 00:15:13,078
ngayong nakuha na ni Max
ang isa sa mga kasangkapan mo.

184
00:15:13,662 --> 00:15:17,791
May mga paraan para mapilitang lumabas
ang soro sa lungga, William.

185
00:15:17,875 --> 00:15:20,294
At tutulungan mo ako.

186
00:15:20,377 --> 00:15:25,049
Gagawin ulit kitang espiya

187
00:15:25,132 --> 00:15:29,094
sa huling pagkakataon.

188
00:15:29,178 --> 00:15:31,555
Hindi mangyayari 'yon.

189
00:15:42,274 --> 00:15:44,777
Kung lalabanan mo…

190
00:15:46,195 --> 00:15:48,739
mas lalo ka lang masasaktan.

191
00:16:15,766 --> 00:16:16,767
Tanga.

192
00:16:21,772 --> 00:16:23,107
-Hoy!
-Ano'ng ginagawa mo?

193
00:16:23,190 --> 00:16:25,275
-Sinisilip ko kung nasa labas siya.
-Wala.

194
00:16:25,359 --> 00:16:28,696
-Pa'no mo nalaman?
-Di kasi siya makakapasok dito. Tara na.

195
00:16:28,779 --> 00:16:32,032
Sabi niya iba na ngayon,
na may ibang paraan na.

196
00:16:32,116 --> 00:16:35,160
Oo, pero puro siya kasinungalingan.
Alam mo na dapat 'yon ngayon.

197
00:16:35,244 --> 00:16:39,915
Ano na'ng gagawin natin? Wala?
Tatanggapin na lang natin?

198
00:16:39,999 --> 00:16:41,375
Wala tayong tatanggapin.

199
00:16:41,458 --> 00:16:43,711
Mabubuhay tayo
hanggang may sumaklolo sa 'tin.

200
00:16:43,794 --> 00:16:45,796
-Si Eleven ba?
-Mm-hmm.

201
00:16:45,879 --> 00:16:47,256
Pa'no mo nalamang siya 'yon?

202
00:16:47,339 --> 00:16:49,633
May alam ka bang ibang may psychic powers

203
00:16:49,717 --> 00:16:52,177
na kayang pasukin 'yong isip ni Vecna,

204
00:16:52,261 --> 00:16:55,097
labanan siya,
gamitin siya para sabihan tayong tumakas?

205
00:16:55,180 --> 00:16:56,306
Si El lang 'yon.

206
00:16:56,390 --> 00:16:59,476
Ibig sabihin, alam niyang nandito tayo
at ililigtas niya tayo.

207
00:16:59,560 --> 00:17:01,645
Wag ka ngang lakad nang lakad.

208
00:17:01,729 --> 00:17:04,273
Naaalala ko sa 'yo 'yong kuya mo, e.

209
00:17:08,235 --> 00:17:09,278
Salamat.

210
00:17:15,659 --> 00:17:17,953
Ba't ba hindi makapasok si Henry dito?

211
00:17:18,037 --> 00:17:19,246
Hindi ko alam.

212
00:17:20,414 --> 00:17:22,750
Dalawang taon kang walang ginagawa.

213
00:17:24,001 --> 00:17:25,461
May theory ka na siguro.

214
00:17:28,797 --> 00:17:31,967
Kung maghihintay lang tayo,
e di mag-usap na tayo.

215
00:17:38,766 --> 00:17:40,142
-Itong kulungan—
-Camazotz.

216
00:17:40,225 --> 00:17:42,269
Camazotz. Oo na.

217
00:17:44,521 --> 00:17:46,940
Gawa 'to sa mga alaala ni Henry, di ba?

218
00:17:47,816 --> 00:17:50,444
Kasama na ang kuwebang 'to.

219
00:17:50,527 --> 00:17:54,031
Kaya naisip ko, para 'tong,

220
00:17:54,698 --> 00:17:56,909
ewan, parang alaala na,
sa kung anong dahilan,

221
00:17:56,992 --> 00:17:59,119
ayaw harapin ni Henry.

222
00:18:00,370 --> 00:18:01,705
Dala siguro ng trauma.

223
00:18:03,415 --> 00:18:07,711
Pero wala namang nakakatakot
sa lugar na 'to, kaya…

224
00:18:08,420 --> 00:18:09,421
baka mali ako.

225
00:18:11,924 --> 00:18:13,509
'Yon ang theory ko.

226
00:18:15,010 --> 00:18:16,011
Ayos 'yon, a.

227
00:18:18,555 --> 00:18:19,389
Salamat.

228
00:18:19,973 --> 00:18:22,851
At kung tama ka,

229
00:18:24,436 --> 00:18:27,439
baka puwede tayong tumakas
gamit ang alaala na 'to.

230
00:18:28,023 --> 00:18:29,358
-Ano?
-Okay, ganito…

231
00:18:30,234 --> 00:18:33,487
'Yong bahay namin, 'yong attic mo,
mga traumatic na alaala rin 'yon,

232
00:18:33,570 --> 00:18:35,447
at may daan 'yon palabas ng Camazotz.

233
00:18:35,531 --> 00:18:38,075
Kaya baka meron din sa alaala ni Henry.

234
00:18:38,158 --> 00:18:41,036
Una sa lahat,
walang kahit na ano dito, gaya ng sabi ko.

235
00:18:41,120 --> 00:18:43,956
Pangalawa, hindi lang basta traumatic
'yong mga alaala natin.

236
00:18:44,039 --> 00:18:47,543
Mga alaala 'yon no'ng mismong sandali
na ninakaw ni Henry ang isip natin.

237
00:18:47,626 --> 00:18:49,711
Di naman niya mananakaw
ang sariling isip niya.

238
00:18:49,795 --> 00:18:53,215
-Pa'no ka nakakasiguro?
-Dahil walang sense 'yon.

239
00:18:53,298 --> 00:18:55,551
Itong lugar ba na 'to, may sense?

240
00:18:57,719 --> 00:18:58,720
Ang akin lang,

241
00:18:59,721 --> 00:19:01,348
baka naman may…

242
00:19:02,182 --> 00:19:04,977
secret passage dito o kung ano.

243
00:19:05,060 --> 00:19:08,355
Oo nga, tama, nakalimutan ko
'yong tungkol sa secret passage.

244
00:19:12,234 --> 00:19:13,235
Ano'ng meron sa labas?

245
00:19:13,318 --> 00:19:15,612
Buhangin. Puro buhangin.

246
00:19:16,280 --> 00:19:17,489
-Nalibot mo na?
-Oo.

247
00:19:17,573 --> 00:19:19,366
-Lahat?
-Ang lawak kaya niyan.

248
00:19:19,950 --> 00:19:20,784
So, hindi pa.

249
00:19:23,871 --> 00:19:25,455
Wag kang lalabas.

250
00:19:25,539 --> 00:19:29,334
Holly, dito lang tayo
at hihintayin natin si Eleven, tapos.

251
00:19:29,418 --> 00:19:32,921
Mukhang seryoso si Henry no'ng sinabi niya
na may paraan para maabot ka niya.

252
00:19:33,005 --> 00:19:35,549
Kailangan nating makaalis dito
bago pa mangyari 'yon.

253
00:19:36,925 --> 00:19:37,843
Sasama ka ba?

254
00:19:38,427 --> 00:19:41,180
O hahayaan mong pumunta sa disyerto
ang isang bata?

255
00:19:42,764 --> 00:19:43,765
Binabawi ko na.

256
00:19:43,849 --> 00:19:47,311
Hindi ko naaalala ang kuya mo sa 'yo.
Kuhang-kuha mo ang kuya mo.

257
00:20:01,241 --> 00:20:02,242
Joyce?

258
00:20:03,660 --> 00:20:04,995
May tumawag ba ng punerarya?

259
00:20:16,465 --> 00:20:17,716
Mike.

260
00:20:21,220 --> 00:20:22,262
El!

261
00:20:22,346 --> 00:20:23,555
Mike…

262
00:20:30,854 --> 00:20:31,855
Nandito na 'ko.

263
00:20:32,981 --> 00:20:34,316
Ligtas ka.

264
00:20:34,399 --> 00:20:35,567
Oo, ligtas ako.

265
00:20:36,652 --> 00:20:37,778
Siya si Kali,

266
00:20:38,654 --> 00:20:39,863
kapatid ko.

267
00:20:39,947 --> 00:20:41,615
Siya siguro 'yong sikat na si Mike.

268
00:20:42,741 --> 00:20:44,660
Hindi… Hindi ko maintindihan.

269
00:20:44,743 --> 00:20:48,163
Mahabang kuwento.
Mas mabuti kung isang sabihan na lang.

270
00:20:49,164 --> 00:20:51,124
Nasa'n na 'yong ibang sasalubong sa 'min?

271
00:20:55,671 --> 00:20:56,880
Nandito lang siya.

272
00:21:04,471 --> 00:21:05,639
Diyos ko po.

273
00:21:06,682 --> 00:21:08,100
Ga'no katagal na siyang ganito?

274
00:21:08,183 --> 00:21:09,268
Ilang oras na.

275
00:21:10,560 --> 00:21:13,021
Mahahanap mo kaya siya?

276
00:21:19,027 --> 00:21:21,613
Nakita mo kung ga'no katagal
bago gumuho 'yong wormhole?

277
00:21:21,697 --> 00:21:22,698
Mga 10, 20 minutes?

278
00:21:22,781 --> 00:21:24,866
Akala ko nga agaran, e. Hindi pala.

279
00:21:24,950 --> 00:21:27,077
-Ba't parang dismayado ka?
-Hindi, a.

280
00:21:27,160 --> 00:21:28,912
-Parang dismayado ka, e.
-Nalilito ako.

281
00:21:28,996 --> 00:21:31,290
Sa nakikita ko,
dalawa lang ang posibilidad.

282
00:21:31,373 --> 00:21:34,001
Puwedeng afterlife na 'to
at kaluluwa na lang tayo,

283
00:21:34,084 --> 00:21:35,210
na mukhang malabo naman.

284
00:21:35,294 --> 00:21:39,423
O baka hindi tuluyang nasira ni Nancy
'yong exotic matter.

285
00:21:39,506 --> 00:21:42,801
Dahil kung nasira niya 'yon,
gumuho na sana 'yong pader ng wormhole

286
00:21:42,884 --> 00:21:44,928
at nahigop na sana tayo sa kawalan.

287
00:21:45,012 --> 00:21:47,055
Okay, so ano pa'ng hinihintay natin?

288
00:21:47,139 --> 00:21:48,181
Sa'n ka pupunta?

289
00:21:48,265 --> 00:21:50,934
Hahanap ako ng signal,
hahanapin ko si Nancy.

290
00:21:51,018 --> 00:21:52,769
-Steve, sandali.
-Tara na, Henderson.

291
00:21:52,853 --> 00:21:54,146
-Sandali!
-Tara na.

292
00:21:54,980 --> 00:21:57,524
Steve, di pa natin alam
kung ligtas sa taas.

293
00:21:57,607 --> 00:21:59,609
Sabi mo di pa sira 'yong exotic matter.

294
00:21:59,693 --> 00:22:03,655
Ang sabi ko, hindi tuluyang nasira
pero malinaw na nagalaw 'yon.

295
00:22:03,739 --> 00:22:07,909
Di natin alam ang magiging epekto nito
sa matter, space-time, gravity.

296
00:22:07,993 --> 00:22:12,456
Baka nga delikado na ang building na 'to,
isang physics-defying death trap.

297
00:22:12,539 --> 00:22:14,166
Mukha namang hindi delikado.

298
00:22:14,249 --> 00:22:16,960
Nancy, copy mo? Jonathan, nandiyan ka ba?

299
00:22:17,961 --> 00:22:18,962
Hello?

300
00:22:22,549 --> 00:22:23,967
Susmaryosep.

301
00:22:32,559 --> 00:22:34,770
Wala naman siguro sila sa taas, 'no?

302
00:22:59,044 --> 00:23:00,629
Naku, naku, naku.

303
00:23:00,712 --> 00:23:01,922
Wag naman po! Nancy!

304
00:23:05,175 --> 00:23:07,594
Nancy! Wag naman.

305
00:23:07,677 --> 00:23:08,637
Nancy!

306
00:23:08,720 --> 00:23:10,806
Sige na. Nancy.

307
00:23:10,889 --> 00:23:12,808
Halika. Halika.

308
00:23:12,891 --> 00:23:15,602
-Okay ka lang? Okay ka lang? Okay.
-Oo. Siguro.

309
00:23:16,603 --> 00:23:17,479
Ano'ng nangyari?

310
00:23:18,313 --> 00:23:19,314
Hindi ko alam.

311
00:23:21,691 --> 00:23:23,068
Nahulog yata tayo.

312
00:23:23,151 --> 00:23:25,195
At mukhang di natin nasira 'yon.

313
00:23:25,278 --> 00:23:26,613
Ginalit lang natin.

314
00:23:29,032 --> 00:23:30,450
Tara. Halika na.

315
00:23:33,078 --> 00:23:34,871
Umalis na tayo dito.

316
00:23:37,499 --> 00:23:39,584
-Nasa'n 'yong pinto?
-'Tang ina.

317
00:23:40,252 --> 00:23:42,337
Ayun. Tara.

318
00:23:46,341 --> 00:23:47,384
'Tang ina!

319
00:23:50,178 --> 00:23:53,723
Hala! 'Tang ina! Patay!

320
00:23:56,643 --> 00:23:58,145
Punyeta.

321
00:23:59,563 --> 00:24:00,856
Ano ba 'to?

322
00:24:22,002 --> 00:24:25,505
Hindi nag-iwan ng note o kahit ano
si Nancy sa simbahan?

323
00:24:25,589 --> 00:24:27,966
Hindi. Walang kahit ano.

324
00:24:28,675 --> 00:24:31,636
Ibig sabihin, mga wala silang pakialam

325
00:24:32,220 --> 00:24:34,097
o kaya nahuli sila ng militar.

326
00:24:34,181 --> 00:24:37,809
Pero para mapanatag ka,
do'n ako sa wala silang pakialam.

327
00:24:37,893 --> 00:24:41,480
Teka, 'yong pader na parang laman,
hindi kaya—

328
00:24:41,563 --> 00:24:44,274
Nahigop sila ng higanteng vacuum
sa kabila? Hindi, e.

329
00:24:45,317 --> 00:24:46,443
Pero ewan ko, Mike.

330
00:24:46,526 --> 00:24:48,528
Pareho lang tayong nalilito.

331
00:24:49,237 --> 00:24:50,280
Lahat ng 'to,

332
00:24:50,363 --> 00:24:54,451
si Max, si Holly, 'yong pader,
konektado lahat 'yon,

333
00:24:54,534 --> 00:24:55,785
pero di ko alam kung pa'no.

334
00:24:55,869 --> 00:24:58,205
Parang may nawawalang piraso sa puzzle, e.

335
00:24:58,872 --> 00:24:59,748
Malaking piraso.

336
00:24:59,831 --> 00:25:03,460
Nasa isip ni Vecna 'yong mga piraso
at may paraan na tayo para makapasok.

337
00:25:03,543 --> 00:25:05,629
Pero wala pang nahahanap si Jane.

338
00:25:06,463 --> 00:25:08,632
Naku! Ayan na si Pollyanna
para pasayahin tayo.

339
00:25:09,591 --> 00:25:11,092
Nahihirapan siya.

340
00:25:11,176 --> 00:25:13,303
Talaga? Baka kailangan niyang mapag-isa.

341
00:25:13,386 --> 00:25:15,472
Humihina siya, hindi lumalakas.

342
00:25:15,555 --> 00:25:18,475
Eksperto ka na kay El ngayon

343
00:25:18,558 --> 00:25:20,977
kahit isa't kalahating araw lang
kayong nagkakilala?

344
00:25:21,061 --> 00:25:23,188
Ang totoo, mas matagal pa sa 'yo.

345
00:25:23,271 --> 00:25:26,983
Sabay kaming lumaki,
at Jane ang pangalan niya.

346
00:25:27,067 --> 00:25:29,027
-Jane Hopper.
-Nandito ako para tumulong.

347
00:25:29,110 --> 00:25:32,197
Nandito ka para tumulong?
Sorry kung di kita mapasalamatan, a?

348
00:25:32,280 --> 00:25:34,115
Sabi mo walang pag-asa ang labang 'to?

349
00:25:34,199 --> 00:25:35,951
Sabi mo walang pag-asa?

350
00:25:36,034 --> 00:25:37,327
Wala akong sinabing gano'n.

351
00:25:37,410 --> 00:25:40,372
Talaga? Gano'n 'yong dating sa 'kin, e.

352
00:25:40,455 --> 00:25:43,250
Nalingat lang ako,
kung ano-ano na'ng pinasok mo sa ulo niya.

353
00:25:43,333 --> 00:25:46,503
Baka kaya siya nahihirapang
hanapin si Will dahil ginulo mo siya.

354
00:25:46,586 --> 00:25:49,464
Naguguluhan siya no'ng nakilala ko siya
dahil sa 'yo.

355
00:25:49,548 --> 00:25:52,384
-Dahil sa mga kasinungalingan mo.
-Lahat ng ginawa ko—

356
00:25:52,467 --> 00:25:55,512
Para protektahan siya.
Sabihin mo 'yan sa sarili mo.

357
00:25:55,595 --> 00:25:58,932
Pero kung gusto mo siyang protektahan,
dapat niyang malaman ang totoo

358
00:25:59,015 --> 00:26:04,062
at dapat handa siya sa lahat
ng posibleng kaharapin niya sa kabila.

359
00:26:04,145 --> 00:26:08,400
-Di 'to matatapos sa pagpatay kay Henry.
-Ano'ng ibig sabihin no'n?

360
00:26:08,483 --> 00:26:13,238
Wala 'yon. Bata lang siya.
Di niya alam ang sinasabi niya.

361
00:26:13,321 --> 00:26:15,115
Puro lang siya kabalbalan.

362
00:26:15,198 --> 00:26:17,158
Alam mong totoo ang sinasabi ko.

363
00:26:18,368 --> 00:26:23,164
Pero gaya ng pagsisinungaling mo kay Jane,
nagsisinungaling ka rin sa sarili mo.

364
00:26:25,125 --> 00:26:27,752
Gusto mong malaman
kung ba't nandito pa 'ko?

365
00:26:29,504 --> 00:26:34,467
Nandito ako para siguraduhin
na hindi na 'to mauulit.

366
00:26:41,057 --> 00:26:41,891
Si El.

367
00:26:46,313 --> 00:26:47,314
El!

368
00:26:48,023 --> 00:26:49,691
Uy, ayos ka lang ba?

369
00:26:50,984 --> 00:26:52,402
Di ko siya maabot.

370
00:26:52,485 --> 00:26:53,695
Pawala-wala siya.

371
00:26:53,778 --> 00:26:55,405
Marami tayong pagkain do'n,

372
00:26:55,488 --> 00:26:58,950
kaya kumain ka, magpahinga ka,
mag-recharge ka muna. Mamaya ulit.

373
00:26:59,034 --> 00:27:00,035
O kaya…

374
00:27:00,952 --> 00:27:02,412
palakasin natin 'yong signal mo.

375
00:27:02,996 --> 00:27:04,039
-'Yong tank.
-Oo.

376
00:27:04,122 --> 00:27:06,750
Matagal ayusin 'yon
pero magre-recharge ka pa naman.

377
00:27:06,833 --> 00:27:08,668
At saka ang hirap gawin no'n

378
00:27:08,752 --> 00:27:10,545
kaya dapat lang na pakinabangan ko.

379
00:27:18,386 --> 00:27:21,181
-Mamaya na 'ko magsa-sign in, a.
-Emotional support lang ako.

380
00:27:21,264 --> 00:27:23,266
Ms. Buckley! Ms. Buckley!

381
00:27:24,309 --> 00:27:25,560
Alam mo…

382
00:27:28,063 --> 00:27:29,981
Uy. Mag-usap tayo.

383
00:27:30,065 --> 00:27:31,733
-Sige.
-Teka, Robin!

384
00:27:31,816 --> 00:27:33,068
Aayusin ko lang muna 'to!

385
00:27:33,151 --> 00:27:34,152
Pa'no 'yong plano?

386
00:27:34,235 --> 00:27:35,403
Vickie.

387
00:27:37,030 --> 00:27:39,783
Alam kong galit ka
at may dahilan ka naman.

388
00:27:39,866 --> 00:27:41,660
-Hinahanap ka nila.
-Nino?

389
00:27:41,743 --> 00:27:43,662
-Ng security, ng militar.
-Bakit?

390
00:27:43,745 --> 00:27:46,122
-Magmamaang-maangan ka pa?
-Ano ba'ng sinasabi mo?

391
00:27:46,206 --> 00:27:47,832
Sige, bibigyan kita ng hint.

392
00:27:47,916 --> 00:27:50,377
Ikaw, sa kuwarto ni Mr. Bailey, benzos.

393
00:27:51,086 --> 00:27:52,504
Kuha mo na?

394
00:27:52,587 --> 00:27:57,467
Robin, sabihin mo sa 'kin
kung ano'ng nangyayari sa 'yo, ngayon na.

395
00:28:03,014 --> 00:28:05,975
Okay, Max, kailangan mo nang umuwi.

396
00:28:21,324 --> 00:28:23,284
Alam mo, kanina pa tayo dito.

397
00:28:23,368 --> 00:28:25,412
Katiting pa lang 'yong napupuntahan natin.

398
00:28:25,495 --> 00:28:27,414
Sa wakas, nagets mo rin.

399
00:28:27,497 --> 00:28:30,542
Di ko alam kung ga'no katagal,
pero matagal akong naghanap dito.

400
00:28:30,625 --> 00:28:33,628
Imposibleng may makita ka
na hindi ko nakita.

401
00:28:33,712 --> 00:28:36,548
Nakuwento ba ng kuya ko
si Tito Eric sa 'yo?

402
00:28:36,631 --> 00:28:37,799
Tito Eric?

403
00:28:37,882 --> 00:28:40,385
Metal detectorist siya.
Alam mo kung ano 'yon?

404
00:28:40,468 --> 00:28:41,761
Naghahanap siya ng metal.

405
00:28:41,845 --> 00:28:43,596
Oo, gamit ang metal detector.

406
00:28:43,680 --> 00:28:47,267
Naghahanap siya sa lupa
ng mga kayamanang naiwan ng mga patay.

407
00:28:47,350 --> 00:28:50,478
Ayun nga, paborito niyang maghanap
sa Indiana Beach Amusement Park.

408
00:28:50,562 --> 00:28:52,647
Ilang taon siyang naghanap do'n,

409
00:28:52,731 --> 00:28:55,066
pero puro mumurahing alahas lang
ang nahanap niya.

410
00:28:55,150 --> 00:28:58,653
Isang araw, pagbukas niya ng diyaryo,
boom, front page,

411
00:28:58,737 --> 00:29:00,864
may turistang nakahanap ng lata

412
00:29:00,947 --> 00:29:04,033
na puno ng gold at silver coins
na million dollars ang halaga.

413
00:29:04,117 --> 00:29:07,328
Sige, hulaan ko,
sa sitwasyong 'to, ako si Tito Eric.

414
00:29:07,412 --> 00:29:08,705
At ako 'yong turista.

415
00:29:19,090 --> 00:29:20,300
Tanga talaga.

416
00:29:37,525 --> 00:29:39,027
"M" ang palatandaan.

417
00:29:43,698 --> 00:29:45,283
-Sa'n ka pupunta?
-May naisip ako.

418
00:29:45,366 --> 00:29:47,285
-Ano?
-Ipapakita ko pag malapit na tayo.

419
00:29:47,368 --> 00:29:49,871
-Holly!
-Sabi mo gusto mong bumalik.

420
00:29:49,954 --> 00:29:51,581
E di sige, babalik na tayo.

421
00:29:54,000 --> 00:29:57,295
Kung naririnig n'yo kami, papunta na kami.
Uulitin ko, papunta na kami.

422
00:29:57,378 --> 00:30:00,298
Steve, dahan-dahan! Mas delikado sa taas.

423
00:30:00,381 --> 00:30:01,841
Kaya bilisan na natin.

424
00:30:01,925 --> 00:30:04,260
Di tayo makakatulong
kung mamamatay tayo. Steve!

425
00:30:13,436 --> 00:30:14,729
Gaya nga ng sabi ko…

426
00:30:20,318 --> 00:30:21,319
Ano ba?

427
00:30:21,820 --> 00:30:22,904
Punyeta!

428
00:30:30,245 --> 00:30:31,663
Ano'ng ginagawa mo?

429
00:30:31,746 --> 00:30:34,999
Sa baba, parang may sundalo
na sumira ng pinto.

430
00:30:41,965 --> 00:30:43,258
Tumabi ka.

431
00:30:47,846 --> 00:30:49,055
Naku po! Umatras ka!

432
00:30:52,308 --> 00:30:53,977
'Tang ina!

433
00:30:54,060 --> 00:30:55,228
Diyos ko po!

434
00:31:01,943 --> 00:31:02,944
Susmaryosep!

435
00:31:05,572 --> 00:31:08,074
Sa mesa! Tumuntong ka sa mesa!

436
00:31:18,459 --> 00:31:19,544
Ano na?

437
00:31:26,009 --> 00:31:28,052
Tulong! Tulong!

438
00:31:28,136 --> 00:31:30,430
-Tulong! Tulong!
-Steve!

439
00:31:30,513 --> 00:31:33,641
-Tulong! Tulong!
-Hoy! Tulong!

440
00:31:33,725 --> 00:31:36,853
-Tulong! Tulong! Tulong!
-Tulong! Tulong! Tulong!

441
00:32:12,013 --> 00:32:13,056
Patapos na kami.

442
00:32:17,143 --> 00:32:18,478
Aayusin 'to ni El.

443
00:32:19,604 --> 00:32:20,813
Aayusin niya 'to.

444
00:32:25,151 --> 00:32:27,236
Ako 'yong nakaisip nito, Hop.

445
00:32:28,571 --> 00:32:29,447
Ako 'yong…

446
00:32:30,031 --> 00:32:32,575
nakaisip na pumasok siya ro'n.

447
00:32:33,159 --> 00:32:35,620
Ewan ko. Siguro naisip ko,

448
00:32:35,703 --> 00:32:40,124
pagkatapos ng nangyari,
no'ng nakita ko 'yong ginawa niya,

449
00:32:40,917 --> 00:32:43,252
naisip ko na baka…

450
00:32:43,336 --> 00:32:46,673
na baka sa kakaprotekta ko sa kanya,

451
00:32:46,756 --> 00:32:49,258
pinipigilan ko lang pala siya

452
00:32:50,927 --> 00:32:53,262
dahil hindi ako nakikinig sa kanya,

453
00:32:53,346 --> 00:32:55,181
hindi ako nagtitiwala.

454
00:32:55,264 --> 00:32:56,683
Kaya kung…

455
00:32:57,809 --> 00:33:01,437
Ewan ko, siguro kung maniniwala
at magpapaubaya ako,

456
00:33:01,521 --> 00:33:04,899
baka-sakaling
maging maayos din ang lahat. At…

457
00:33:06,234 --> 00:33:11,364
Pakiramdam ko kasi,
lahat na lang ng desisyon ko, mali.

458
00:33:11,447 --> 00:33:12,490
Alam ko.

459
00:33:13,992 --> 00:33:18,162
Mapipilit mo sila
sa mga sitwasyong hindi pa nila kaya.

460
00:33:18,246 --> 00:33:20,832
Puwede kang maging tulad 'ko,
overprotective,

461
00:33:20,915 --> 00:33:23,251
pero magtatanim naman sila
ng sama ng loob sa 'yo.

462
00:33:23,334 --> 00:33:25,837
Joyce, ang isa sa mga saya
ng pagiging magulang…

463
00:33:28,381 --> 00:33:30,842
ay ang walang katapusang paalala

464
00:33:30,925 --> 00:33:32,719
na bawat desisyong ginawa mo,

465
00:33:33,511 --> 00:33:34,971
mali pala.

466
00:33:38,433 --> 00:33:40,101
Di mo kasalanan 'to, Joyce.

467
00:33:42,979 --> 00:33:44,230
Di mo kasalanan 'to.

468
00:33:59,871 --> 00:34:02,165
Ang ganda niyan, a.
Galing kay Murray 'yan?

469
00:34:02,874 --> 00:34:03,875
Oo.

470
00:34:05,626 --> 00:34:07,545
Magaling palang pumili si Santa.

471
00:34:11,966 --> 00:34:14,385
Uy. Kanina pala sa Squawk,

472
00:34:15,136 --> 00:34:17,597
may sinabing weird si Kali.

473
00:34:17,680 --> 00:34:20,850
Hindi raw 'to matatapos
kahit mapatay natin si Henry.

474
00:34:20,933 --> 00:34:22,685
Ano'ng ibig niyang sabihin?

475
00:34:23,728 --> 00:34:25,146
Wala 'yon.

476
00:34:25,855 --> 00:34:27,190
Paiinitin ko lang 'to.

477
00:34:27,815 --> 00:34:31,027
Okay, kung wala lang 'yon,
bakit galit si Hop sa kanya?

478
00:34:31,110 --> 00:34:33,279
-Wala nga.
-Ang kaibigan, dapat tapat.

479
00:34:33,362 --> 00:34:35,573
-Di ako nagsisinungaling.
-Umiiwas ka, e.

480
00:34:35,656 --> 00:34:37,658
Ang daya mo. Gusto ko lang tumulong.

481
00:34:37,742 --> 00:34:40,203
Wala kang matutulong dito.

482
00:34:40,286 --> 00:34:42,288
Ako ang makakapagsabi no'n.

483
00:34:44,248 --> 00:34:45,208
El, dali na.

484
00:34:50,379 --> 00:34:52,924
May lab sa Upside Down.

485
00:34:53,007 --> 00:34:55,551
Binubuhay ulit nila 'yong program ni Papa.

486
00:34:56,511 --> 00:34:58,262
Gumagawa sila ng bagong numbers.

487
00:35:01,974 --> 00:35:03,059
'Yong militar?

488
00:35:06,437 --> 00:35:07,396
Okay.

489
00:35:07,897 --> 00:35:11,943
Ganito, pag napatay na natin si Vecna,
sisirain natin 'yong bagong lab.

490
00:35:12,026 --> 00:35:13,736
Tapos ang program. Parang side quest.

491
00:35:13,820 --> 00:35:16,239
Mike, hindi mo naiintindihan.

492
00:35:16,322 --> 00:35:19,450
Di nila kailangan ng lab
para gumawa ng bagong numbers.

493
00:35:19,534 --> 00:35:20,827
'Yong dugo ni Henry.

494
00:35:22,495 --> 00:35:23,704
Nananalaytay 'yon sa 'kin.

495
00:35:23,788 --> 00:35:25,498
Hindi ako halimaw.

496
00:35:26,749 --> 00:35:28,209
Alam ko na 'yon ngayon.

497
00:35:28,793 --> 00:35:30,837
Pero gamit ako, gamit ang dugo ko,

498
00:35:32,004 --> 00:35:34,382
makakagawa sila ng marami pang halimaw.

499
00:35:35,508 --> 00:35:37,718
Ng marami pang Henry.

500
00:35:38,302 --> 00:35:40,263
Di titigil ang militar
sa paghahanap sa 'yo.

501
00:35:40,346 --> 00:35:43,391
Alam natin 'yon.
Kaya nga aalis tayo sa Hawkins, e.

502
00:35:43,474 --> 00:35:46,352
Pagkatapos nito, aalis na tayo.

503
00:35:46,435 --> 00:35:49,313
Tatakas tayo sa malayong lugar. Di ba?

504
00:35:49,397 --> 00:35:51,566
Sa lugar na di nila tayo mahahanap.

505
00:35:52,316 --> 00:35:55,444
Sa lugar na merong kahit isang waterfall.

506
00:35:56,445 --> 00:35:57,363
Mike.

507
00:35:59,240 --> 00:36:02,493
Di 'to katulad ng campaigns mo.

508
00:36:03,619 --> 00:36:05,371
Di ikaw ang magdidikta ng katapusan.

509
00:36:05,955 --> 00:36:07,540
Hindi ngayon.

510
00:36:09,125 --> 00:36:10,334
Baka nga hindi ako.

511
00:36:11,419 --> 00:36:12,670
Pero tayo.

512
00:36:12,753 --> 00:36:16,215
Ikaw, ako, si Lucas, si Will,
at si Dustin.

513
00:36:16,799 --> 00:36:18,342
Dahil kuwento natin 'to.

514
00:36:19,468 --> 00:36:21,804
At sisimulan natin sa pagbawi kay Will.

515
00:36:38,154 --> 00:36:38,988
Max.

516
00:36:49,165 --> 00:36:52,418
Di mo na kailangan ng spyglass.
Kuweba ko 'yan.

517
00:36:52,501 --> 00:36:53,336
Kaya nga.

518
00:36:53,419 --> 00:36:54,962
Saka may takip pa 'yan.

519
00:36:55,463 --> 00:36:56,297
Kaya nga.

520
00:36:57,381 --> 00:36:58,299
Tingnan mo.

521
00:36:59,717 --> 00:37:00,801
Nang may takip.

522
00:37:06,098 --> 00:37:07,975
Okay, sobrang dilim.

523
00:37:08,059 --> 00:37:09,060
Pero hindi gaano.

524
00:37:09,143 --> 00:37:10,645
Kita mo 'yong hugis ng liwanag?

525
00:37:10,728 --> 00:37:12,897
Kapareho siya ng hugis
ng entrance ng kuweba.

526
00:37:12,980 --> 00:37:15,524
Nagkataon lang ba
na kahugis no'ng butas 'yong kuweba,

527
00:37:15,608 --> 00:37:17,318
kuweba na pinuntahan dati ni Henry?

528
00:37:17,401 --> 00:37:20,696
Tingin ko mapa 'yong takip
na ginawa ni Henry no'ng bata siya,

529
00:37:20,780 --> 00:37:23,199
mapa na dadalhin tayo
sa isang secret location.

530
00:37:24,033 --> 00:37:26,702
Kailangan lang nating pagtapatin
'yong mga hugis.

531
00:37:27,536 --> 00:37:30,039
Ano namang matatagpuan natin
sa secret location na 'yon?

532
00:37:30,122 --> 00:37:31,582
Traumatic memory ni Henry?

533
00:37:31,666 --> 00:37:34,168
Oo. At saka 'yong daan palabas
ng Camazotz.

534
00:37:35,044 --> 00:37:37,296
'Yon ang theory ko.

535
00:37:38,256 --> 00:37:39,715
-Ayos, a.
-Salamat.

536
00:37:39,799 --> 00:37:42,009
Kaso may maliit na butas 'yong theory mo.

537
00:37:42,093 --> 00:37:44,804
Malapit lang tayo sa secret location,
at may mata ako,

538
00:37:44,887 --> 00:37:48,140
pero puro buhangin lang ang nakikita ko.

539
00:37:50,977 --> 00:37:51,852
Kumapit ka!

540
00:37:52,645 --> 00:37:53,896
Kumapit ka!

541
00:38:12,748 --> 00:38:14,083
"M" ang palatandaan.

542
00:38:22,717 --> 00:38:25,803
Vic, di ka ba magsasalita?

543
00:38:25,886 --> 00:38:28,889
Di ko kasi mabasa
'yong sinasabi ng mukha mo, e.

544
00:38:28,973 --> 00:38:32,935
Alam kong masyadong mabigat,
lalo na kung isang bagsakan lang.

545
00:38:33,561 --> 00:38:35,479
Mga halimaw at alternate dimensions,

546
00:38:35,563 --> 00:38:39,150
tapos alam ko na medyo unethical
'yong pagdodroga ko sa mga Turnbow—

547
00:38:39,233 --> 00:38:42,028
Tama na, Robin. Please, tama na.

548
00:38:42,111 --> 00:38:44,113
Ilang beses kong sinubukang
sabihin sa 'yo.

549
00:38:44,196 --> 00:38:47,992
Hindi, nagsinungaling ka.
At nagsinungaling ka nang paulit-ulit.

550
00:38:48,075 --> 00:38:50,369
-Sabi ko na may mali, e.
-Kaya nga! Sorry na!

551
00:38:50,453 --> 00:38:54,040
"Daming ganap sa work. Tawag ako bukas."
"Sorry, may problema sa Squawk."

552
00:38:54,123 --> 00:38:56,459
Sino ba'ng magtatrabaho magdamag
sa radio station?

553
00:38:56,542 --> 00:38:59,378
At sinong tanga ang maniniwala do'n?

554
00:38:59,462 --> 00:39:00,963
E di ako, si Vickie,

555
00:39:01,047 --> 00:39:03,549
na mukhang tanga kakatunganga sa telepono,

556
00:39:03,632 --> 00:39:05,509
habang nag-aadik kayo ng barkada mo.

557
00:39:05,593 --> 00:39:06,719
Nag-aadik?

558
00:39:06,802 --> 00:39:10,348
Umamin ka na, Robin.
Alam ko na nagwi-withdrawal ka.

559
00:39:10,431 --> 00:39:12,266
Mali ka. Hindi ako nagda-drugs.

560
00:39:12,350 --> 00:39:14,060
-Sige, sorry, a.
-Tingnan mo ako!

561
00:39:14,143 --> 00:39:17,730
Busy ka nga pala sa paghahanap ng halimaw
kasama ng mga barkada mo.

562
00:39:17,813 --> 00:39:20,191
Diyos ko! Sige, baka 'yon talaga
ang paniwala mo.

563
00:39:20,274 --> 00:39:23,736
Sa dami ng tinira mo,
kung bigla kang hihinto,

564
00:39:23,819 --> 00:39:26,072
puwede kang malito,
ma-paranoid, mag-hallucinate—

565
00:39:26,155 --> 00:39:28,991
Hindi ako nagha-hallucinate!

566
00:39:29,075 --> 00:39:30,785
Sige. Ulitin nga natin.

567
00:39:30,868 --> 00:39:32,995
-Bale, may dark wizard.
-Oo.

568
00:39:33,079 --> 00:39:34,455
-Kinidnap 'yong mga bata.
-Oo.

569
00:39:34,538 --> 00:39:36,999
-Tapos dinala sila sa dream world.
-Tama.

570
00:39:38,459 --> 00:39:42,129
Vickie, nahati na sa apat 'yong mundo.

571
00:39:42,213 --> 00:39:44,757
Militar na ang namamahala sa lugar natin.

572
00:39:44,840 --> 00:39:47,301
Kabaliwan pa rin ba 'yong sinasabi ko?

573
00:39:48,511 --> 00:39:49,804
Sobra!

574
00:39:49,887 --> 00:39:52,515
Alam mo kung ano'ng sinasabi ng mukha ko?

575
00:39:52,598 --> 00:39:54,100
-Oo.
-Galit.

576
00:39:54,183 --> 00:39:59,355
Galit na may kurot,
at sobrang nag-aalangang kurot,

577
00:39:59,438 --> 00:40:00,314
ng pag-aalala.

578
00:40:01,232 --> 00:40:03,442
Dahil kahit na galit na galit ako
sa 'yo ngayon,

579
00:40:03,526 --> 00:40:06,779
masama ang lagay mo, Robin,
at kailangan mo ng tulong.

580
00:40:06,862 --> 00:40:08,823
Kailangan mo ng totoong tulong.

581
00:40:09,740 --> 00:40:12,076
-May tumawag tungkol sa ninakaw na drugs.
-Teka.

582
00:40:12,159 --> 00:40:13,202
Nakita mo ba siya?

583
00:40:13,285 --> 00:40:14,286
Si Robin Buckley?

584
00:40:14,370 --> 00:40:17,248
Oo, nandito siya.
Nakita ko siyang pumasok do'n.

585
00:40:19,417 --> 00:40:20,626
Vickie, sorry talaga.

586
00:40:20,709 --> 00:40:21,544
Wag.

587
00:40:21,627 --> 00:40:23,129
-Kailangan ko nang umalis.
-Robin!

588
00:40:23,838 --> 00:40:24,755
Hoy!

589
00:40:25,923 --> 00:40:27,133
Hoy, kinakausap kita!

590
00:40:27,800 --> 00:40:28,717
Buckley, huminto ka!

591
00:40:32,638 --> 00:40:34,265
Sa'n ka pupunta?

592
00:40:36,684 --> 00:40:39,019
-Tulong!
-Tulong!

593
00:40:39,103 --> 00:40:40,938
-Tulong!
-Dustin!

594
00:40:41,021 --> 00:40:42,690
-Tulong! Steve!
-Hoy!

595
00:40:46,193 --> 00:40:47,278
Ayun, o.

596
00:40:49,780 --> 00:40:53,826
Ano'ng ginagawa mo?
Hindi 'yan gagana. Tumigil ka nga!

597
00:40:53,909 --> 00:40:57,121
Steve, tumigil ka.
Seryoso ako. Delikado 'yan.

598
00:40:57,204 --> 00:40:59,665
-Matutumba ka.
-Oo, delikado. Gets ko na, okay?

599
00:40:59,748 --> 00:41:02,334
Wag! Wag ka ngang kupal!

600
00:41:02,418 --> 00:41:04,128
Hindi ako kupal. Pupuntahan ko sila!

601
00:41:04,211 --> 00:41:07,173
Lagi mong pinapahamak ang sarili mo
at di na puwedeng maulit 'yon!

602
00:41:07,256 --> 00:41:08,841
Wag ka namang masyadong makasarili.

603
00:41:08,924 --> 00:41:11,802
Kung pupunta ka do'n, mamamatay ka,
at di ko na kakayanin 'yon.

604
00:41:11,886 --> 00:41:14,221
Di ka puwedeng mamatay,
di ko na kakayanin.

605
00:41:14,305 --> 00:41:18,267
Wag mo nang hayaang maulit 'yon.
Please, wag mo nang hayaang maulit 'yon.

606
00:41:19,393 --> 00:41:20,394
Wag ikaw.

607
00:41:21,520 --> 00:41:22,605
Sorry.

608
00:41:22,688 --> 00:41:23,898
Hindi, okay lang.

609
00:41:35,743 --> 00:41:37,369
-Tulong!
-Tulong!

610
00:41:37,870 --> 00:41:39,997
-Ano ba? Tulong!
-Tulong!

611
00:41:40,831 --> 00:41:42,041
Hala, hala!

612
00:41:42,124 --> 00:41:43,626
Upo. Umupo ka. Umupo ka.

613
00:41:45,252 --> 00:41:47,963
-Ano'ng ginagawa natin?
-Para kalat 'yong bigat natin.

614
00:41:48,047 --> 00:41:49,924
Sabi ni Mr. Goldstein sa physics.

615
00:41:50,007 --> 00:41:52,343
Magkakaro'n tayo ng konting oras.

616
00:41:53,511 --> 00:41:55,471
Narinig na siguro nila tayo ngayon.

617
00:41:55,554 --> 00:41:57,097
E, ba't di sila sumasagot?

618
00:41:57,181 --> 00:41:59,433
Kung narinig man nila tayo,
ano'ng magagawa nila?

619
00:41:59,517 --> 00:42:01,393
Basta. Kahit ano.

620
00:42:06,857 --> 00:42:08,025
Di sila darating.

621
00:42:08,108 --> 00:42:09,568
Wag mong sabihin 'yan.

622
00:42:09,652 --> 00:42:11,237
Gusto mo 'yong totoo, di ba?

623
00:42:31,298 --> 00:42:32,758
Ayoko sa The Clash.

624
00:42:35,052 --> 00:42:35,928
Ano?

625
00:42:38,389 --> 00:42:40,516
Ayoko sa The Clash.

626
00:42:40,599 --> 00:42:44,311
Tuwing pinapatugtog mo 'yon,
lumalayo ako sa totoong mundo.

627
00:42:46,355 --> 00:42:48,983
Sige. Ayokong nagbabasa ng articles mo.

628
00:42:49,066 --> 00:42:50,901
Hindi naman opinyon ko ang gusto mo.

629
00:42:50,985 --> 00:42:54,029
-Gusto mo lang sabihin kong maganda 'yon.
-Maganda naman, a.

630
00:42:54,113 --> 00:42:55,155
Kadalasan.

631
00:42:55,239 --> 00:42:56,532
Kadalasan…

632
00:42:56,615 --> 00:42:58,117
Wow. Okay.

633
00:42:59,243 --> 00:43:01,662
Di ko binasa 'yong Slaughterhouse-Five.

634
00:43:01,745 --> 00:43:04,290
Binasa ko 'yong CliffsNotes
tapos kunwari nagustuhan ko.

635
00:43:04,373 --> 00:43:05,749
Ako rin, sa Anna Karenina.

636
00:43:05,833 --> 00:43:08,294
'Yong CliffsNotes din ako
tapos kunwari nagustuhan ko.

637
00:43:08,377 --> 00:43:10,879
Lagi kang saktong six minutes late,

638
00:43:10,963 --> 00:43:14,842
di ko lang sinasabi,
pero gusto ko nang suntukin 'yong pader.

639
00:43:14,925 --> 00:43:16,927
Dinala ko 'yong pink sweater mo
sa Goodwill.

640
00:43:17,011 --> 00:43:19,972
-Ano? Hinahanap ko 'yon, a.
-Alam mo namang ayoko ng pink.

641
00:43:20,055 --> 00:43:22,474
Pero na-guilty naman ako pagkatapos.

642
00:43:22,558 --> 00:43:26,145
Flinush ko 'yong huling balot
ng Purple Palm Tree Delight sa toilet

643
00:43:26,228 --> 00:43:27,896
at hindi ako na-guilty.

644
00:43:27,980 --> 00:43:30,149
-Grabe naman.
-Naiinis ako pag high ka.

645
00:43:30,232 --> 00:43:31,358
Ayoko pag lasing ka.

646
00:43:31,442 --> 00:43:34,403
Mas naiinis ako pag high ka
tapos lasing ako.

647
00:43:34,486 --> 00:43:35,738
Ayoko rin no'n.

648
00:43:36,363 --> 00:43:38,032
Ba't ba natin ginagawa 'yon?

649
00:43:41,410 --> 00:43:42,494
Ewan ko ba.

650
00:43:51,211 --> 00:43:52,963
Di ako nag-apply sa Emerson.

651
00:43:55,090 --> 00:43:56,008
Alam ko.

652
00:43:57,885 --> 00:43:59,595
Ba't wala kang sinabi?

653
00:44:00,846 --> 00:44:02,264
Ba't wala kang sinabi?

654
00:44:06,060 --> 00:44:07,186
Di ako sigurado, e.

655
00:44:12,983 --> 00:44:14,693
Pakiramdam ko kasi…

656
00:44:16,570 --> 00:44:17,988
may mali sa ginagawa ko.

657
00:44:21,533 --> 00:44:24,787
Para bang di ako sumusunod
sa normal na takbo ng buhay.

658
00:44:26,455 --> 00:44:27,665
Alam mo na,

659
00:44:29,041 --> 00:44:30,626
sa dami ng pinagdaanan natin…

660
00:44:31,669 --> 00:44:33,629
'Yong shared trauma natin?

661
00:44:35,422 --> 00:44:36,298
Oo.

662
00:44:38,342 --> 00:44:42,429
Pa'no 'to maiintindihan ng iba?

663
00:44:42,513 --> 00:44:43,806
Parang ito…

664
00:44:44,890 --> 00:44:46,558
ito 'yong bagay na…

665
00:44:47,976 --> 00:44:50,145
nagdudugtong sa 'tin habambuhay.

666
00:44:51,021 --> 00:44:52,022
Alam mo 'yon?

667
00:44:54,149 --> 00:44:56,151
Napapanatag ako.

668
00:44:57,277 --> 00:44:58,487
Pero…

669
00:45:00,864 --> 00:45:01,782
Ewan ko ba.

670
00:45:02,783 --> 00:45:04,159
Nakakasakal din minsan.

671
00:45:05,911 --> 00:45:06,787
Tama.

672
00:45:10,916 --> 00:45:15,087
No'ng spring break, no'ng nasa Lenora ka…

673
00:45:16,672 --> 00:45:19,299
di ko naman talaga kailangang magpaiwan
dahil sa trabaho.

674
00:45:19,383 --> 00:45:21,969
Nando'n naman si Fred.

675
00:45:24,430 --> 00:45:26,682
Pero 'yon yata ang dahilan
kaya di ako sumama.

676
00:45:28,183 --> 00:45:29,893
'Yong pakiramdam na…

677
00:45:30,728 --> 00:45:32,354
kailangan ko ng space.

678
00:45:34,565 --> 00:45:36,942
Space para may makasama kang iba?

679
00:45:41,989 --> 00:45:43,532
Mabuting tao si Steve.

680
00:45:45,451 --> 00:45:46,744
Napapatawa niya 'ko.

681
00:45:47,870 --> 00:45:52,458
At mas lamang 'yong hairstyle niya sa 'yo.
Lamang na lamang.

682
00:45:53,333 --> 00:45:54,251
Pero hindi.

683
00:45:56,879 --> 00:45:59,173
Hindi, iba 'yong sa amin.

684
00:45:59,757 --> 00:46:01,633
Magkaiba kami.

685
00:46:01,717 --> 00:46:05,429
Alam mo kung ano'ng sabi niya sa 'kin?
Gusto niya ng anim na anak.

686
00:46:05,512 --> 00:46:06,638
Anim na anak?

687
00:46:06,722 --> 00:46:08,891
Anim na tsikiting.

688
00:46:09,767 --> 00:46:11,101
Happy Meal na 'yon, e.

689
00:46:12,686 --> 00:46:13,854
Pero ang point ko…

690
00:46:15,481 --> 00:46:18,942
alam niya kung ano'ng gusto niya
at maganda 'yon.

691
00:46:19,026 --> 00:46:20,110
Pero ako,

692
00:46:21,195 --> 00:46:22,070
hindi ko alam.

693
00:46:23,989 --> 00:46:24,865
At…

694
00:46:25,866 --> 00:46:28,911
umasa siguro ako
na may oras pa 'kong alamin 'yon.

695
00:46:30,162 --> 00:46:32,706
-Kaso…
-Nahati sa apat 'yong mundo.

696
00:46:32,790 --> 00:46:33,957
Tapos ngayon…

697
00:46:36,835 --> 00:46:37,836
Tapos ngayon…

698
00:46:42,549 --> 00:46:43,383
Uy.

699
00:46:48,764 --> 00:46:50,682
May isa pa 'kong aaminin.

700
00:46:51,767 --> 00:46:52,684
Malaki 'to.

701
00:46:59,691 --> 00:47:01,235
John Coltrane.

702
00:47:01,860 --> 00:47:06,156
Marami na 'kong naging pagkukulang sa 'yo.

703
00:47:08,450 --> 00:47:11,328
Maganda siguro na kahit sa huli,
makabawi man lang ako.

704
00:47:12,371 --> 00:47:13,205
Eto, o.

705
00:47:31,348 --> 00:47:32,766
Nancy Wheeler.

706
00:47:35,310 --> 00:47:36,520
Puwede mo ba akong…

707
00:47:38,272 --> 00:47:39,231
hindi…

708
00:47:40,107 --> 00:47:41,108
pakasalan?

709
00:47:48,115 --> 00:47:50,075
Sinabi ko sa sarili ko

710
00:47:51,451 --> 00:47:53,287
na kahit papa'no

711
00:47:54,079 --> 00:47:55,622
maaayos nito ang lahat.

712
00:47:55,706 --> 00:47:58,333
Pero mas lalo lang lalala, e.

713
00:47:59,459 --> 00:48:04,506
Kaya di ko mahugot-hugot 'yan sa bulsa ko
nitong huling dalawang araw.

714
00:48:07,301 --> 00:48:08,552
Ano'ng masasabi mo?

715
00:48:12,723 --> 00:48:14,766
Tatanggapin mo ba 'yong un-proposal ko?

716
00:48:15,976 --> 00:48:18,103
Tinatanggap ko 'yong un-proposal mo.

717
00:48:20,397 --> 00:48:21,523
Minahal kita.

718
00:48:22,816 --> 00:48:23,984
Mahal kita,

719
00:48:24,818 --> 00:48:25,944
Nancy Wheeler.

720
00:48:27,446 --> 00:48:29,823
Mahal kita, Jonathan Byers.

721
00:49:05,609 --> 00:49:06,610
Diyos ko.

722
00:49:15,911 --> 00:49:16,954
Jonathan!

723
00:49:17,663 --> 00:49:18,538
Diyos ko po!

724
00:49:21,625 --> 00:49:22,626
Salamat.

725
00:49:49,653 --> 00:49:50,904
Salamat, ha.

726
00:49:50,988 --> 00:49:52,572
Hahanapin ko siya.

727
00:49:54,074 --> 00:49:55,701
Iuuwi ko siya.

728
00:50:03,375 --> 00:50:06,211
Okay. Tandaan mo,
kung gusto mo nang lumabas…

729
00:50:35,574 --> 00:50:37,409
Will, nandito ako.

730
00:50:39,327 --> 00:50:41,747
Ipakita mo sa 'kin kung nasa'n ka.

731
00:50:43,373 --> 00:50:45,208
Ipakita mo kung nasa'n ka.

732
00:51:06,313 --> 00:51:07,189
Will.

733
00:51:10,609 --> 00:51:11,526
Will.

734
00:51:12,194 --> 00:51:13,403
Naririnig mo 'ko?

735
00:51:13,487 --> 00:51:14,738
Will, gising!

736
00:51:42,974 --> 00:51:44,059
Pahiram nga ako.

737
00:51:51,983 --> 00:51:53,610
Tingin mo may nahulog dito?

738
00:51:58,031 --> 00:52:00,700
Alaala lang 'to, di ba?

739
00:52:00,784 --> 00:52:02,661
Walang mananakit sa 'tin dito.

740
00:52:02,744 --> 00:52:04,079
Walang mananakit sa 'tin.

741
00:52:18,009 --> 00:52:19,302
Diyan ka lang sa likod ko.

742
00:52:19,386 --> 00:52:21,304
-Sabi mo—
-Alam ko kung ano'ng sinabi ko.

743
00:52:33,400 --> 00:52:34,776
Pa'no mo 'ko nahanap?

744
00:52:37,112 --> 00:52:39,114
Pa'no mo 'ko nahanap?

745
00:52:39,197 --> 00:52:40,448
Nakikita niya tayo.

746
00:52:40,532 --> 00:52:42,117
Bakit niya tayo nakikita?

747
00:52:42,200 --> 00:52:43,368
Di kita sasaktan.

748
00:52:44,035 --> 00:52:46,830
Wag po, sir, wag mo 'kong babarilin.

749
00:52:46,913 --> 00:52:48,665
-Sino ka?
-Henry.

750
00:52:48,748 --> 00:52:50,834
Ako si Henry Creel. Tagadito lang ako.

751
00:52:50,917 --> 00:52:52,961
-Sino'ng nagpadala sa 'yo?
-Wala.

752
00:52:53,044 --> 00:52:53,962
Pinadala ka nila.

753
00:52:54,045 --> 00:52:56,506
-Nasa kuweba ako. Tapos may sumigaw.
-Pinadala ka nila!

754
00:52:56,590 --> 00:52:59,217
Nagkakamali po kayo.
Kailangan n'yo ng doktor.

755
00:53:13,773 --> 00:53:15,650
Wag po! Wag!

756
00:53:24,159 --> 00:53:25,076
Holly!

757
00:53:26,077 --> 00:53:26,995
Holly!

758
00:53:31,416 --> 00:53:32,417
Letse!

759
00:53:34,336 --> 00:53:36,880
Uy, wag kang matakot.

760
00:53:36,963 --> 00:53:41,343
Bakit binaril no'ng lalaki si Henry?
Gusto lang naman niyang tumulong.

761
00:53:41,426 --> 00:53:43,345
-Ewan ko.
-Kaya ba naging masama si Henry?

762
00:53:43,428 --> 00:53:45,805
Ewan ko. Tapos na 'yon, okay?

763
00:53:45,889 --> 00:53:47,641
Kailangan na nating umalis.

764
00:54:37,482 --> 00:54:38,692
Tama ka.

765
00:54:38,775 --> 00:54:41,528
'Yong daan palabas ng Camazotz,
nandito nga.

766
00:54:50,453 --> 00:54:51,288
Max?

767
00:55:01,840 --> 00:55:08,555
Gagawin kitang espiya
sa huling pagkakataon.

768
00:55:20,066 --> 00:55:21,067
Huli ka.

769
00:55:22,861 --> 00:55:26,489
Will. Will, kumalma ka.
Kumalma ka. Nandito ako.

770
00:55:26,573 --> 00:55:27,574
-El…
-Nandito ako.

771
00:55:27,657 --> 00:55:28,825
El… El…

772
00:55:28,908 --> 00:55:32,412
Ako 'to. Ako 'to.
Nandito ako para iuwi ka. Kalma na.

773
00:55:32,495 --> 00:55:35,623
Sinubukan ko siyang pigilan,
pero wala akong nagawa.

774
00:55:35,707 --> 00:55:36,708
Nakita niya.

775
00:55:37,292 --> 00:55:39,002
Ang ano? Ano'ng nakita niya?

776
00:55:39,711 --> 00:55:40,628
Si Max.

777
00:55:41,838 --> 00:55:43,381
Alam na niya kung nasa'n si Max.

778
00:55:44,090 --> 00:55:45,925
At pinapunta niya sila do'n.

779
00:55:46,718 --> 00:55:49,387
Pupuntahan nila si Max. Sa Hawkins.

780
00:55:53,350 --> 00:55:54,476
-El!
-Ano'ng nangyari?

781
00:55:54,559 --> 00:55:55,560
Ayos ka lang ba?

782
00:55:56,186 --> 00:55:58,521
-Ano'ng nangyari?
-Ayos lang si Will?

783
00:55:59,397 --> 00:56:00,982
Papatayin ni Vecna si Max.

784
00:56:02,484 --> 00:56:04,569
Kailangan nating pumunta
sa ospital, ngayon na.

785
00:56:04,652 --> 00:56:07,364
Hoy! Wala ba kayong naririnig?
Nagwi-withdrawal siya.

786
00:56:07,447 --> 00:56:08,865
-Hindi nga!
-Alam n'yo ba 'yon?

787
00:56:08,948 --> 00:56:11,034
Sa ospital siya dapat, hindi sa kulungan.

788
00:56:11,117 --> 00:56:13,161
Aba, akalain mo 'yon?
Nasa ospital na siya.

789
00:56:13,244 --> 00:56:16,581
Hawkins 'to, Candy Cane.
Di siya ang kauna-unahang adik.

790
00:56:21,419 --> 00:56:23,338
Nagloloko 'yong kuryente sa ospital.

791
00:56:23,922 --> 00:56:26,216
Yari si Lola. Bahala sila diyan.

792
00:56:26,299 --> 00:56:27,884
Di n'yo gets. Umalis na tayo dito.

793
00:56:27,967 --> 00:56:30,678
Wala kaming dapat gawin.
Lumakad ka na, adik.

794
00:56:30,762 --> 00:56:32,138
Hindi ako adik.

795
00:56:32,222 --> 00:56:34,432
Kung di tayo lalabas dito ngayon din,

796
00:56:34,516 --> 00:56:36,476
mamamatay tayong lahat.

797
00:56:36,559 --> 00:56:41,147
Kahit ano pa'ng sabihin mo,
makukulong ka pa rin.

798
00:56:41,231 --> 00:56:42,982
Kaya wag ka nang magsayang ng boses.

799
00:56:43,066 --> 00:56:45,860
-Lumabas na tayo dito.
-Wala akong dapat gawin.

800
00:56:48,446 --> 00:56:49,322
Susmaryosep!

801
00:56:49,406 --> 00:56:50,407
Takbo!

802
00:57:13,513 --> 00:57:15,056
Hindi tayo ang hinahanap nila.

803
00:57:15,140 --> 00:57:16,099
Ha? Ano?

804
00:57:16,182 --> 00:57:19,185
Hindi tayo ang hinahanap nila.
May iba pang daan palabas?

805
00:57:19,269 --> 00:57:21,563
Sa basement.
Sa staff parking ang labas no'n.

806
00:57:23,690 --> 00:57:24,691
Okay.

807
00:57:25,233 --> 00:57:27,277
Dali na, Lucas, sumagot ka. Sumagot ka.

808
00:57:30,280 --> 00:57:31,823
Sumagot ka. Ano ba?

809
00:57:31,906 --> 00:57:33,324
-English, marunong sila?
-Hindi.

810
00:57:33,408 --> 00:57:34,993
-Wag mo nang i-private.
-Ano?

811
00:57:36,411 --> 00:57:38,621
Lucas, si Robin 'to.
May papuntang Demo diyan.

812
00:57:38,705 --> 00:57:41,833
Naririnig mo? May papuntang Demo diyan.
Itakas mo na si Max.

813
00:57:41,916 --> 00:57:43,835
Mag-elevator ka. Do'n sa may hagdan.

814
00:57:43,918 --> 00:57:45,253
Magkita tayo sa basement.

815
00:58:12,113 --> 00:58:13,156
Dali na. Dali na.

816
00:58:23,208 --> 00:58:24,292
Pakshet.

817
00:58:25,543 --> 00:58:26,503
Putik. Dali na!

818
00:58:44,521 --> 00:58:46,022
Lintik naman, o!

819
00:58:47,732 --> 00:58:48,942
Di ko matulak.

820
00:58:49,025 --> 00:58:51,277
Susubukan nating lumusot, okay?

821
00:58:51,361 --> 00:58:52,362
Halika.

822
00:58:58,076 --> 00:58:59,077
Ayos ka lang?

823
00:58:59,160 --> 00:59:00,537
-Ayos lang ako.
-Okay.

824
00:59:04,249 --> 00:59:06,668
-Hilahin mo 'yong kamay ko, okay?
-Okay.

825
00:59:30,400 --> 00:59:31,276
Hala! Diyos ko po!

826
00:59:31,359 --> 00:59:32,819
Sige na. Nasa likod ko sila.

827
00:59:32,902 --> 00:59:34,612
-Umalis na tayo.
-Saan tayo?

828
00:59:35,446 --> 00:59:38,116
Dito! Ano ba'ng nangyayari?

829
00:59:39,409 --> 00:59:41,035
-Dito!
-Pa'no nila tayo nahanap?

830
00:59:41,119 --> 00:59:42,829
Ewan, pero kailangan nating umalis.

831
00:59:42,912 --> 00:59:43,788
Sige. Tara na.

832
00:59:43,871 --> 00:59:45,707
-Tara. Bilis.
-Dali, dali, dali.

833
00:59:45,790 --> 00:59:48,209
Bilis. 'Yong pinto. Isara mo 'yong pinto!

834
00:59:50,670 --> 00:59:52,714
-'Tang ina.
-Dali! Deretso lang!

835
00:59:53,673 --> 00:59:54,966
-Tara.
-Punyeta!

836
00:59:55,049 --> 00:59:56,634
Bilisan na natin!

837
00:59:57,719 --> 01:00:00,471
-'Yong pinto! Buksan n'yo 'yong pinto!
-Bilis!

838
01:00:05,393 --> 01:00:07,729
Putsa. Dito tayo! Tara! Bilis!

839
01:00:07,812 --> 01:00:08,771
Umupo kayo!

840
01:00:18,072 --> 01:00:20,783
Pasensiya na kung inisip ko na adik ka.

841
01:00:22,035 --> 01:00:26,623
Sorry kung matagal na panahon
akong nagsinungaling sa 'yo.

842
01:00:27,123 --> 01:00:30,710
Para lang malaman mo,
totoo 'yong sinabi ko tungkol sa Enzo's.

843
01:00:30,793 --> 01:00:35,548
At kung himala man na makaligtas tayo,
dadalhin talaga kita do'n,

844
01:00:35,632 --> 01:00:39,552
tapos magde-dessert tayo. Deal?

845
01:01:05,286 --> 01:01:06,704
Patayin na natin 'yan.

846
01:01:06,788 --> 01:01:10,291
Hindi puwede. Hindi puwede.
Wag. Babalik na si Max.

847
01:01:10,875 --> 01:01:12,043
Kailangan.

848
01:01:13,044 --> 01:01:14,337
Babalik siya.

849
01:01:21,344 --> 01:01:22,470
Ayos ka lang?

850
01:01:24,013 --> 01:01:24,972
-Sige na.
-Okay.

851
01:01:35,692 --> 01:01:36,734
Okay.

852
01:01:40,530 --> 01:01:42,407
Handa ka nang umuwi, turista?

853
01:01:45,076 --> 01:01:46,035
Oo naman.

854
01:04:25,695 --> 01:04:26,737
Lucas.

855
01:04:33,452 --> 01:04:34,996
Holly. Sandali.

856
01:04:37,206 --> 01:04:38,374
Di ka puwedeng sumama.

857
01:04:38,457 --> 01:04:41,252
Ano? Ano'ng ibig mong sabihin?

858
01:04:41,335 --> 01:04:42,837
Ito 'yong daan papunta sa 'kin,

859
01:04:43,588 --> 01:04:44,547
sa katawan ko,

860
01:04:44,630 --> 01:04:46,340
hindi sa 'yo.

861
01:04:46,424 --> 01:04:48,050
Hanapin mo 'yong daan mo.

862
01:04:48,134 --> 01:04:51,679
Pa'no? Wala akong Kate Bush.
Di ko naman kilala si Kate Bush.

863
01:04:51,762 --> 01:04:53,764
Di mo kailangan si Kate Bush
para makalabas.

864
01:04:53,848 --> 01:04:55,766
Ako rin pala, hindi.

865
01:04:55,850 --> 01:04:57,977
Hindi lang music ang daan pabalik.

866
01:04:58,686 --> 01:05:03,149
Kailangan mo ng bagay na mag-uugnay sa 'yo
sa totoong mundo, sa pamilya mo.

867
01:05:03,816 --> 01:05:05,651
'Yong malakas,

868
01:05:06,235 --> 01:05:07,486
makabuluhan.

869
01:05:07,570 --> 01:05:11,198
Si Lucas, no'ng hinawakan niya
'yong kamay ko sa ospital,

870
01:05:12,158 --> 01:05:13,200
naramdaman ko siya.

871
01:05:13,784 --> 01:05:14,744
Dito.

872
01:05:16,120 --> 01:05:18,581
Pero naramdaman ko rin dito.

873
01:05:19,290 --> 01:05:20,875
Wala naman akong boyfriend, e.

874
01:05:20,958 --> 01:05:22,293
Di mo kailangan ng boyfriend.

875
01:05:22,376 --> 01:05:24,420
Kailangan mo lang ng bagay
na espesyal sa 'yo,

876
01:05:24,503 --> 01:05:27,548
'yong nakakapagpakalma sa 'yo,

877
01:05:27,632 --> 01:05:31,677
'yong nagpapalakas sa 'yo,
'yong nagbibigay sa 'yo ng pag-asa.

878
01:05:32,261 --> 01:05:33,471
Holly the Heroic.

879
01:05:33,554 --> 01:05:35,097
Kasama mo siya ngayon.

880
01:05:36,599 --> 01:05:38,768
Pero kasama mo rin siya sa totoong mundo.

881
01:05:38,851 --> 01:05:40,144
Kung nasa'n ka man,

882
01:05:40,227 --> 01:05:42,772
kailangan mo lang siyang sundan pauwi.

883
01:05:42,855 --> 01:05:43,940
Pa'no?

884
01:05:44,690 --> 01:05:49,612
Alalahanin mo lang
kung ano'ng halaga niya sa 'yo.

885
01:05:50,655 --> 01:05:52,865
Wala naman siyang halaga, e.

886
01:05:55,076 --> 01:05:56,369
Laruan lang siya.

887
01:05:57,453 --> 01:06:00,331
Kung laruan lang siya,
bakit lagi mo siyang dala?

888
01:06:00,414 --> 01:06:01,332
Si Mike.

889
01:06:01,958 --> 01:06:05,586
Sabi niya may divine powers daw
si Holly the Heroic at matapang siya,

890
01:06:05,670 --> 01:06:09,632
at kung matatakot ako,
puwede akong maging siya.

891
01:06:09,715 --> 01:06:11,300
Sinusubukan ko,

892
01:06:11,384 --> 01:06:13,219
pero walang nangyayari, e.

893
01:06:15,262 --> 01:06:17,515
Kahit ano'ng gawin ko, ako pa rin 'to.

894
01:06:19,600 --> 01:06:22,186
'Yong batang di makatulog
nang walang ilaw.

895
01:06:22,269 --> 01:06:25,147
No'ng inatake 'yong mama ko,
di ko siya nailigtas.

896
01:06:25,231 --> 01:06:26,691
Di ko nailigtas 'yong sarili ko.

897
01:06:26,774 --> 01:06:28,359
Holly, umatras ka!

898
01:06:29,610 --> 01:06:31,529
Nakatayo lang ako.

899
01:06:31,612 --> 01:06:33,531
Tapos no'ng inatake ka ni Henry…

900
01:06:34,198 --> 01:06:35,408
Tama na!

901
01:06:35,908 --> 01:06:37,159
Nakatayo na naman ako.

902
01:06:37,743 --> 01:06:40,746
Pa'no naging heroic 'yon?

903
01:06:41,330 --> 01:06:44,208
Wala kang magagawa
no'ng mga oras na 'yon, Holly.

904
01:06:44,291 --> 01:06:47,378
Wheeler ka. Matalino ka.

905
01:06:48,129 --> 01:06:51,716
Tingin mo mapipigilan ng fire poker mo
'yong mga halimaw?

906
01:06:52,299 --> 01:06:55,094
May nakakalimutan kang mahahalagang bagay.

907
01:06:55,177 --> 01:06:57,888
No'ng araw na nagkita tayo,
pumunta ka sa gubat

908
01:06:57,972 --> 01:07:00,558
kahit na sinabi sa 'yo ni Henry
na may mga halimaw do'n.

909
01:07:00,641 --> 01:07:03,019
Tapos sinundan mo ako sa kuweba

910
01:07:03,102 --> 01:07:05,688
kahit wala kang dahilan
para pagkatiwalaan ako.

911
01:07:05,771 --> 01:07:08,941
Tapos no'ng pinabalik kita kay Henry,

912
01:07:09,025 --> 01:07:10,484
sa panganib,

913
01:07:10,568 --> 01:07:11,861
di ka nag-alinlangan.

914
01:07:11,944 --> 01:07:15,823
Tapos kanina,
hindi ka sumuko kahit suko na 'ko.

915
01:07:17,408 --> 01:07:19,535
Ang tagal ko na dito, Holly.

916
01:07:20,911 --> 01:07:21,996
Sobrang tagal na.

917
01:07:24,040 --> 01:07:25,875
At di ako makalabas-labas.

918
01:07:27,793 --> 01:07:28,711
Pero ikaw?

919
01:07:30,046 --> 01:07:32,381
Nakahanap ka ng daan palabas ng Camazotz.

920
01:07:32,465 --> 01:07:33,716
Dahil sa 'yo…

921
01:07:35,092 --> 01:07:37,094
makikita ko na 'yong mga kaibigan ko.

922
01:07:37,887 --> 01:07:39,638
Makikita ko na si Lucas.

923
01:07:41,182 --> 01:07:43,476
Niligtas mo ako, Holly Wheeler.

924
01:07:44,977 --> 01:07:46,062
Niligtas mo ako.

925
01:07:48,314 --> 01:07:52,610
Kaya hindi lang basta laruan
si Holly the Heroic.

926
01:07:54,528 --> 01:07:56,030
Ikaw siya, Holly.

927
01:07:57,698 --> 01:07:58,699
Ikaw siya.

928
01:08:18,719 --> 01:08:20,513
Pa'no mo nalamang gagana 'yon?

929
01:08:22,264 --> 01:08:23,724
Di ko talaga alam.

930
01:08:26,060 --> 01:08:30,523
Mahaba pa 'yong lalakbayin mo.
Di ko alam kung sa'n ka magigising.

931
01:08:30,606 --> 01:08:32,691
Pero malamang hawak ka ni Vecna
sa Upside Down.

932
01:08:32,775 --> 01:08:36,946
Tandaan mo, 'yong Upside Down,
para lang siyang Hawkins.

933
01:08:37,029 --> 01:08:39,949
Kaya pumunta ka sa bahay n'yo
at magtago ka do'n.

934
01:08:40,032 --> 01:08:42,284
Hahanapin ka namin. Okay?

935
01:08:58,759 --> 01:09:00,219
Kita na lang tayo sa kabila.

936
01:09:00,886 --> 01:09:02,012
Sa kabila.

937
01:12:27,134 --> 01:12:29,136
Nagsalin ng Subtitle: Faith Dela Cruz

